<article id="post-910" class="post-910 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-casinos tag-hotels tag-las-vegas tag-nevada tag-usa tag-weddings tag-westjet">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/03/on-my-way-home/" rel="bookmark">On my way home</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Well, the wedding&#8217;s done, Tamara and Dan are wed, and pretty much everyone is pooped. The bridal party was out late the night before, the groom&#8217;s group was fairly tired, and I&#8217;m just beat from all the running around. My feet are killing me.<br />
It wasn&#8217;t the shortest wedding I&#8217;ve been to, but it was definitely more expedient than most of the ones I&#8217;ve seen. That said, it was still a lovely ceremony.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/03/on-my-way-home/#more-910" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;On my way home&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/03/on-my-way-home/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2008-03-10T01:06:02-06:00">10 March 2008</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/casinos/" rel="tag">casinos</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/hotels/" rel="tag">hotels</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/las-vegas/" rel="tag">las vegas</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/nevada/" rel="tag">nevada</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/usa/" rel="tag">usa</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/weddings/" rel="tag">weddings</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/westjet/" rel="tag">westjet</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/03/on-my-way-home/#comments">4 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on On my way home</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
